entries.femaleVariant: I can't ignore this anymore. You know what I'm talkin' about.
Keep tellin' yo'self that. But you ain't gon' do nothin' about it.
What, you think because you work with corpos you're suddenly untouchable?
That too. Main reason, though, is you don't stab your l'il sis in the back!
D'you even realize the hell you're puttin' mom through?
Nuh-uh, don't drag momma into this. Without my eddies, she'd've croaked forever ago.
